    "id": "q-ai-pocketflow-0002",
    "title": "PocketFlow 如何用 Shared State、Branch 与 Loop Guard 表达一个可控的 Agent Loop",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "多 Agent 框架扩展",
    "topic": "state-branching-retry-agent-loop",
    "type": "系统设计题",
