    "id": "q-ai-case-0031",
    "title": "当 AI 编程 Agent 改动范围失控时，排障为什么要先看计划和 writable scope，而不是先重写代码",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 场景案例",
    "topic": "context-loading-plan-diff-scope-control",
