    "id": "q-ai-pattern-0030",
    "title": "为什么 Model Routing 必须先做 Capability Gating，再谈 Graceful Degradation 和 Tiered Inference",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 工程模式",
    "topic": "model-routing-capability-gating-graceful-degradation",
