    "id": "q-ai-pattern-0033",
    "title": "为什么 Tool Failure 不能简单理解成重试问题，而必须先定义 Failure Semantics 和 Idempotency",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 工程模式",
    "topic": "tool-failure-semantics-idempotency-side-effect-recovery",
    "type": "运维治理题",
