    "id": "q-ai-pattern-0047",
    "title": "为什么 Agent 安全必须把 Guardrails、Moderation、HITL 和硬边界做成同一控制面",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 工程模式",
    "topic": "guardrails-moderation-hitl-defense-in-depth-safety",
    "type": "原理题",
