    "title": "什么时候应该继续用 n8n，什么时候应该把开放式子任务交给更重的 Agent Runtime",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 平台与工作流",
    "topic": "ai-workflow-performance-observability-boundary-selection",
