    "id": "q-ai-openclaw-0002",
    "title": "OpenClaw 为什么必须把 Workspace、Plugins、Cron 和 Heartbeat 放进同一套治理模型里",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent 平台与工作流",
    "topic": "workspace-skills-plugins-active-task-governance",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
