    "id": "q-ai-agent-foundations-0004",
    "title": "为什么 Stop Policy 不是异常处理细节，而是最小 Agent 的运行时合同",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Agent Runtime 基础",
    "topic": "session-memory-checkpoint-stop-policy",
    "type": "系统设计题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
