    "id": "q-ai-semantic-kernel-0004",
    "title": "为什么 Semantic Kernel 的 Process Framework 比多 Agent 协调更适合某些企业流程",
    "track": "ai-agents",
    "component": "Semantic Kernel",
    "topic": "process-orchestration-observability",
