    "id": "q-bigdata-delta-0017",
    "title": "Delta 排障时，为什么要先把问题归类到冲突、保留、Schema/feature、布局或恢复副作用？",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Delta Lake",
    "topic": "troubleshooting",
    "type": "故障恢复题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
