    "id": "q-bigdata-flink-0009",
    "title": "Flink 失败后为什么有时只重启局部，有时却整作业重启",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Flink",
    "topic": "failover",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
