    "id": "q-bigdata-hive-0005",
    "title": "Hive 里的 Partition 和 Bucketing 为什么不是同一类优化",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "partition-bucketing-and-layout",
    "type": "原理题",
