    "title": "为什么 Hive 的 SerDe 题不能只答“建表时指定个格式”，而必须继续讲 InputFormat、OutputFormat 和 ObjectInspector",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "serde-inputformat-outputformat-objectinspector-row-format",
    "type": "原理题",
