    "id": "q-bigdata-hive-0015",
    "title": "为什么 Hive 小文件治理在 ORC 场景里要讲 CONCATENATE，而且它不是简单重写全量数据",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "orc-stripes-indexes-bloom-filters-small-file-merge",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
