    "title": "为什么 Hive 的 LOAD DATA 题不能只答“把文件导入表里”，而必须继续讲 copy/move、HS2 LOCAL 路径和 rewrite 边界",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "dml-load-insert-dynamic-partitions-write-boundaries",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
