    "id": "q-bigdata-hive-0026",
    "title": "为什么 Hive ACID 题不能只答“支持 UPDATE/DELETE”，而必须继续讲 base、delta 和 read-time merge",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "acid-base-delta-row-id-snapshot-read-path",
    "type": "原理题",
