    "title": "为什么 Hive Metastore 部署题必须区分 embedded、remote service 和 standalone，而不能只说“起一个 HMS”",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "metastore-embedded-remote-standalone-schema-governance",
    "type": "原理题",
