    "id": "q-bigdata-hive-0031",
    "title": "为什么 Hive 的 metadata drift 题不能只答 MSCK REPAIR TABLE，而必须区分 external table、notification 和 synchronized cache",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Hive",
    "topic": "metastore-cachedstore-notification-metadata-drift-boundaries",
    "type": "原理题",
