    "id": "q-bigdata-spark-0016",
    "title": "生产环境里为什么很多 Spark 作业更适合 cluster mode，而不是 client mode",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Spark",
    "topic": "deployment-choice",
    "type": "对比题",
