    "title": "为什么 Spark 的 join 题不能只答“小表广播、大表 sort merge”，而必须继续讲 hint、build side 和 AQE",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Spark",
    "topic": "join-algorithm-selection-broadcast-sort-merge-shuffled-hash",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
