    "id": "q-bigdata-spark-0028",
    "title": "为什么 Spark 的列式缓存和 pruning 题，不能只答“只扫需要的列，所以更快”",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Spark",
    "topic": "columnar-cache-scan-pruning-sql-runtime-footprint",
    "type": "原理题",
    "difficulty": "高级",
