    "id": "q-bigdata-spark-0029",
    "title": "为什么 Structured Streaming 的 trigger 题不能只答“每隔几秒跑一次”，而必须继续讲 micro-batch、AvailableNow、continuous 和 foreachBatch",
    "track": "big-data",
    "component": "Spark",
