    "title": "LLM 推理能力为什么不等于形式证明，CoT、ReAct、搜索和验证怎么讲",
    "track": "llm-foundations",
    "component": "llm-reasoning",
    "topic": "cot-self-consistency-react-tree-of-thoughts-verification",
